org.nlpcraft.model.builder

Class NCElementBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpcraft.model.builder.NCElementBuilder

  • public class NCElementBuilder
extends Object
    Model element builder for NCElement instances.

    To use this builder start by invoking one of the following static method to create new builder instance:
    • newElement(String)
    • newElement()
    • newElement(String, String)
    Once you have the builder instance you can set all necessary properties and finally call build() method to get properly constructed NCElement instance. Note that at the minimum the element ID must be set.
